<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the seats. Row M: on four seats at west end. Row U.i: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.48</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.20</measure>. Row U.ii <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.41</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.16</measure>. Row V: on two seats at west end; design <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.20</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.19</measure>. Row X: along the edge, which is broken, of two seats at east end. </p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Row M: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.12-0.18</measure>; lunate sigma. Row V: Letters <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.07-0.10</measure>; square sigma, cursive omega. Row X: shallow, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.10-0.12</measure>.</p>
</div>
